      <p class="article-subtitle">The easiest way to feel right is to argue against a weak version of the opposing view. The most honest — and most useful — approach is the opposite: build the strongest case against your own position, then see if it still holds.</p>
      <div class="author-info">
        <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name">{author}</span>
        </span>
        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime={datePublished}>May 9, 2026</time>
      </div>
    </header>

